---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="New Doula? Set Up Your Practice in One Place"
  description="Just certified? Get organized from day one. TJB Pro Mode gives you client plans, visit tracking, notes, and invoicing — built specifically for birth work."
  canonical="https://truejoybirthing.com/new-doula-start-here"
>
  <section class="bg-tjb-warm pt-16 pb-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">New Doula? Set Up Your Practice in One Place.</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-tjb-soft">The tool new doulas wish they'd had on Day One — client management, birth plans, and simple invoicing, built for birth work.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 prose">
      <h2>Why New Doulas Love Pro Mode</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Your clients build their birth plan in the free app — it flows straight into your dashboard</li>
        <li>Track visits and tasks in one organized place (no more scattered notes)</li>
        <li>Send simple invoices connected to client records</li>
        <li>Everything is designed for birth work — not general admin</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Download the True Joy Birthing app</li>
        <li>Activate Pro Mode when you're ready ($29.99/mo or $274.99/yr)</li>
        <li>Invite your clients to download — their plans appear in your dashboard automatically</li>
        <li>Look like a pro from day one</li>
      </ol>

      <div class="text-center my-8">
        <a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/true-joy-birthing" class="inline-block bg-tjb-forest text-tjb-cream px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-tjb-sage transition">
          Download the App — Start Pro
        </a>
        <p class="text-xs text-tjb-soft mt-2">Subscription managed in-app via Apple/Google</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
